title: ScEnvMetaEntry
description:
ScEnvMetaEntry is an XDR Union defines as:

```text union SCEnvMetaEntry switch (SCEnvMetaKind kind) { case SC_ENV_META_KIND_INTERFACE_VERSION: struct { uint32 protocol; uint32 preRelease; } interfaceVersion; }; ```

ScEnvMetaEntryInterfaceVersion.description:
